PN,31301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FThe Government should look at
OL,7,Fincreasing universal credit for 66-
OL,8,Fyear-olds to prevent financial
OL,9,Fhardship stemming from the "lottery of
OL,10,Flife" as the state pension age rises
OL,11,Fto 67, according to a committee of MPs.
OL,13,FThe Work and Pensions Committee said
OL,14,Fit is backing calls for the Government
OL,15,Fto increase universal credit for 66-
OL,16,Fyear-olds.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FIt said ministers should consult on
OL,7,Fthe change with a view to putting it
OL,8,Fin place by the end of 2026 as a
OL,9,Ftemporary measure, allowing time to
OL,10,Fdevelop longer-term support.
OL,12,FThere is evidence the longer wait for
OL,13,Ftheir state pension will "harm" 66-
OL,14,Fyear-olds who are unable to keep
OL,15,Fworking until 67, the committee said.
OL,17,FThe state pension age has started a
OL,18,Fphased rise, gradually increasing in
OL,19,Fsteps from 66 to 67, affecting new
OL,20,Fpensioners.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FThe report said: "For many, this will
OL,7,Fbe a year of hardship, on inadequate
OL,8,Fworking age benefits, potentially
OL,9,Fdepleting savings they were relying on
OL,10,Fto support them in retirement."
OL,12,FThe committee said a growing number of
OL,13,F66-year-olds may have to rely on the
OL,14,Fstandard rate of universal credit of
OL,15,Faround #425 a month for longer,
OL,16,Fdespite worsening health.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FIts report added: "On balance we
OL,7,Fsupport increasing the level of
OL,8,Funiversal credit (UC) for all
OL,9,Frecipients in the year before state
OL,10,Fpension age because it has a greater
OL,11,Fimpact in reducing poverty and
OL,12,Fhardship.
OL,14,F"We recommend it as a short-term
OL,15,Fapproach, to mitigate the impact of
OL,16,Fthe increase to 67, which has already
OL,17,Fstarted.
OL,19,F"We propose using UC on the basis that
OL,20,Fit should enable support to be
OL,21,Fprovided quickly.
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"We recognise that the impact on work
OL,7,Fincentives is a consideration.
OL,8,FHowever, the proposal is for a modest
OL,9,Fincrease in support in the year before
OL,10,Fstate pension age.
OL,12,F"Those out of the labour market at
OL,13,Fthis point in their lives are very
OL,14,Funlikely to return to it."
OL,16,FPeople on low incomes can apply for
OL,17,Fpension credit ` but this support is
OL,18,Fonly available once people have
OL,19,Freached state pension age.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FThe committee said this leaves many
OL,7,Fpre-pensioners, particularly those
OL,8,Fwith health issues, caring
OL,9,Fresponsibilities or long histories in
OL,10,Flabour-intensive jobs, relying on the
OL,11,Fsavings they may have set aside for
OL,12,Fretirement.
OL,14,FThere is also a geographical
OL,15,Fconsideration, with ill-health and
OL,16,Fdisability concentrated in the most
OL,17,Fdeprived areas, where there are fewer
OL,18,Feconomic opportunities, the committee
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FThe report said: "The impacts of the
OL,7,Frise to 67 will be very uneven.
OL,9,F"For many unable to keep working,
OL,10,Fparticularly on low incomes and in the
OL,11,Fmost deprived areas, it will mean
OL,12,Fhardship as they wait longer for a
OL,13,Fstate pension.
OL,15,F"Their shorter life expectancy means
OL,16,Fthat they can then expect to receive
OL,17,Fit for a shorter time than those in
OL,18,Fthe least deprived areas.
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"We know that the last increase ` from
OL,7,F65 to 66 ` resulted in absolute
OL,8,Fpoverty rates among 65-year-olds more
OL,9,Fthan doubling."
OL,11,FThe report also said: "We were
OL,12,Fconcerned to hear that, while later
OL,13,Fworking is generally good for health
OL,14,Fwhen it is voluntary, this is not the
OL,15,Fcase when it is due to financial
OL,16,Fnecessity, particularly for people
OL,17,Fhaving to continue to in physically
OL,18,Fdemanding jobs."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]sD@WOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FIt added: "Based on the evidence we
OL,7,Fhave received, there is a clear
OL,8,Fjustification for providing additional
OL,9,Fsocial security support for those
OL,10,Funable to keep working in the years
OL,11,Fapproaching state pension age.
OL,13,F"While pension age rises have been
OL,14,Fjustified on grounds of fairness
OL,15,Fbetween generations ` each generation
OL,16,Fshould expect to spend a similar
OL,17,Fproportion of adult life contributing
OL,18,Fto and receiving the state pension `
OL,19,Ffairness within generations is also
OL,20,Fimportant."
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FCommittee chairwoman Debbie Abrahams
OL,7,Fsaid: "We can't just allow people who
OL,8,Fare already struggling as they
OL,9,Fapproach pension age to be forced to
OL,10,Fchoose between continuing work in poor
OL,11,Fhealth or prolonging their poverty as
OL,12,Fthey wait for their state pension to
OL,13,Fkick in.
OL,15,F"This is not the later life that
OL,16,Fanyone wants or to see their loved
OL,17,Fones endure after providing for
OL,18,Fdecades.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"We should recognise that pre-
OL,7,Fpensioners have greater needs and
OL,8,Fgreater barriers into employment due
OL,9,Fto ill-health, age discrimination,
OL,10,Flack of opportunity to upskill.
OL,12,F"More than half of people are not in
OL,13,Fpaid work in their mid-60s, and
OL,14,Fthey're not likely to get it if
OL,15,Fthey've been effectively written off.
OL,17,F"Additional social security payments
OL,18,Fare essential in reducing the
OL,19,Fcompounding effects of the lottery of
OL,20,Flife and the state pension age
OL,21,Fincrease."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FAndrea Barry, deputy director for work
OL,7,Fat the Centre for Ageing Better, said:
OL,8,F"What is being proposed by the
OL,9,Fcommittee is a short-term measure to
OL,10,Falleviate the current issue.
OL,12,F"In the longer term, and well before
OL,13,Fany future state pension rises, we
OL,14,Fneed the Government to take a joined-
OL,15,Fup approach across pensions, work,
OL,16,Fbenefits, and health, to ensure that
OL,17,Fthe mid-60s is not a period of
OL,18,Fheightened financial precarity for
OL,19,Fgrowing numbers of older people.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"This will require ensuring that
OL,7,Fongoing reforms to employment and
OL,8,Fskills support are designed with the
OL,9,Fneeds of older people in mind,
OL,10,Falongside enhanced careers guidance
OL,11,Fand financial planning advice for
OL,12,Folder workers, and stronger support
OL,13,Ffor those living with health
OL,14,Fconditions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FA Department for Work and Pensions
OL,7,F(DWP) spokesperson said: "We welcome
OL,8,Fthe Work and Pensions Select Committee
OL,9,Finquiry on the transition to state
OL,10,Fpension age and will consider their
OL,11,Freport and recommendations in due
OL,12,Fcourse.
OL,14,F"As of February 2026, just 0.02% of
OL,15,Fthe universal credit caseload was aged
OL,16,F65 or 66.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"A range of options for extra support
OL,7,Fare available for those that have not
OL,8,Freached state pension age, such as
OL,9,Funiversal credit and other means-
OL,10,Ftested and disability-related
OL,11,Fbenefits, while the Pensions
OL,12,FCommission is examining how we can
OL,13,Fensure secure retirements for
OL,14,Ftomorrow's pensioners."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,FCaroline Abrahams, charity director at
OL,7,FAge UK, said: "We're delighted that
OL,8,Fthe select committee has recognised
OL,9,Fthat far too many people approaching
OL,10,Ftheir state pension age find
OL,11,Fthemselves in a very difficult
OL,12,Ffinancial position.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783784902
OL,3,CMPs back benefit boost for 66-year-
OL,4,Colds as state pension age increases
OL,6,F"Allowing people who are realistically
OL,7,Fnever going to work again to struggle
OL,8,Fto make ends meet until they hit state
OL,9,Fpension age is a senseless waste and
OL,10,Fan issue we've been highlighting for
OL,11,Fmany years, so it's fantastic that the
OL,12,Fcommittee is strongly advising the
OL,13,FGovernment to address it and to do so
OL,14,Fquickly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
